I guess it all depends on how you ride this wave.

text: The thing is.. regardless of the greed of individuals in top positions, money ultimately moves towards value creation. Even if Indian govt had printed ton of money (which they thankfully didn't do as much as US) and given 1lac to all Indians barring top 10%, ultimately these individuals will either keep it in bank or spend it, which is helping either the bank or that business to grow. Very few in India will put most of it in market and get wealthy along with these businesses. Better fix our act first before pointing fingers as in their shoes most of us would have done the same thing
